Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.43,0:00:03.31,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Filling in the distance between hate and love...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.31,0:00:04.86,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The deductions and the suspense of two people!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.06,0:00:06.56,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A difficult case in search of the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.56,0:00:08.23,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A courtroom clash between Kisaki and the prosecution!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.65,0:00:10.23,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.23,0:00:12.03,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.03,0:00:14.08,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:44.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An onsen, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:47.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We haven't been to one in so long, have we?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:51.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it's fall leaf-viewing season now, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.79,0:01:52.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.88,0:01:57.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I recommend this open-air bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.76,0:02:00.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They say this onsen is really good for the body!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.89,0:02:05.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom, you have to take a break from work once in a while and just relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.77,0:02:07.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:08.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kuriyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:12.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What does my schedule look like for next month?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.23,0:02:17.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The current court case is scheduled to be resolved next week, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.94,0:02:20.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's left depends on what you decide as far as the issue of the duty roster...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:21.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.74,0:02:22.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:24.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you would bring the documents for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:25.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.04,0:02:29.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's a duty roster?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.79,0:02:36.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sometimes there are defendants who cannot employ the services of a lawyer due to financial reasons and such.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.42,0:02:42.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's when the government appoints an attorney, but when none of us wants the case, it's left to the duty roster.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.64,0:02:45.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.31,0:02:50.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've only given the case a quick glance-over, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.27,0:02:53.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder why no one chose to take it on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.52,0:02:56.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like the defendant has a decent case here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:02:59.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it's because the opponent is unfavorable?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:00.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The opponent?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:04.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one heading this case is Prosecutor Kujou.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:08.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.58,0:03:11.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Madonna of Prosecutors, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.17,0:03:18.92,Title,,0,0,0,,COURTROOM CONFRONTATION II: KISAKI VS KUJOU\N(PART ONE)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.38,0:03:20.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:23.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should we say we're occupied and refuse it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.58,0:03:27.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Kisaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.46,0:03:29.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of a case is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:32.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's something that occurred about a month ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.80,0:03:37.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The body of a company's president was found in his office in Haido City.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.34,0:03:41.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the fingerprints and the articles left inside the room...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.60,0:03:45.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were able to apprehend the defendant—a habitual offender that had broken into many establishments.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:49.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't seem like a case that would end up in court...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.27,0:03:51.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.81,0:03:55.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the defendant had already admitted to breaking in, being discovered by the victim...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:59.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And against his better judgment, hitting the victim in the head with the ashtray during the struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:02.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he problem is with the charge listed on the indictment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.62,0:04:03.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The charge?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.29,0:04:07.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the indictment, it is charged as a robbery-murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.96,0:04:09.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.42,0:04:12.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But in that case, wouldn't it be an accidental death?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:14.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.21,0:04:18.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I find it hard to imagine Prosecutor Kujou would have made such a mistake, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:20.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kuriyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.59,0:04:24.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I already have the prosecutorial and fact-falsehood memos, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.01,0:04:26.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I still lack the conditional examination papers—could you get them for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:29.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll also need a copy of the autopsy report.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.19,0:04:32.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.31,0:04:34.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:38.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Due to this, the onsen will have to wait for another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.57,0:04:43.30,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Tokyo Detention Center
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:45.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me confirm once more with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.62,0:04:47.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the night of the incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.58,0:04:51.08,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,You broke the window to the Ootsu Real Estate Company's office on the second floor of the Nomoto Building...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.58,0:04:51.08,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Inoue Takashi (55)\NSuspect
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:52.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And proceeded to enter the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.04,0:04:57.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While you were searching around the office, and trying to open the safe in the company president's office...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.42,0:05:04.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were discovered by the company's president, Ootsu Toshiyuki, when he returned for business purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.35,0:05:11.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, during the struggle, you used the glass ashtray to strike him in the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.94,0:05:16.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All this resulting in death.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.07,0:05:18.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is all correct, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.24,0:05:20.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:23.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened to the money in the safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.41,0:05:24.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.70,0:05:27.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, according to testimony from the company employees...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.24,0:05:31.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The 12,000,000 yen in cash taken in that day from a real estate transaction had disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.75,0:05:38.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The prosecution believes that, after you killed President Ootsu, you opened the safe and stole the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.84,0:05:40.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.01,0:05:41.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really don't know anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:44.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's certainly true that the money wasn't found in your room, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.39,0:05:51.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Given that your fingerprints were found on the dial of the safe, the prosecution's suspicions aren't entirely baseless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.85,0:05:53.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really didn't take the money...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.94,0:05:55.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And about that person...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.31,0:05:56.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That person?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:05:58.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you know the victim beforehand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:11.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How many times did you strike the victim's head?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.41,0:06:12.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:14.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was it one time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:15.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two times?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.63,0:06:17.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.13,0:06:20.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, I was surprised and discovered unexpectedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.05,0:06:26.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to the autopsy, there are traces of the victim having been struck three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:29.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it was the third that proved to be the fatal blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:32.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it were a single time, it'd be best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.43,0:06:36.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But with two or three times, the possibility exists that you would be regarded as having intended to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.19,0:06:39.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.61,0:06:40.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:47.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am your ally, so even if it's unfavorable towards your case, please tell me everything honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.66,0:06:51.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me confirm once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.58,0:06:55.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really didn't intend to kill the victim, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.37,0:06:56.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.08,0:06:58.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.17,0:07:01.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In court, we shall press that one point in our argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.13,0:07:03.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.59,0:07:06.95,Signs,,0,0,0,,Tokyo District Court
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.59,0:07:08.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The defendant Inoue Takashi, at approximately 20:30 hours on the night of the incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:11.95,Signs,,0,0,0,,The Case of the Robbery-Murder of the Real Estate Company President\NFirst Public Hearing
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:13.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the second floor of the Nomoto Building in Haido City Block 3-2-9...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.27,0:07:15.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Broke the window of the Ootsu Real Estate president's office and trespassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.02,0:07:18.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While searching for money and other goods...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.69,0:07:25.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was discovered by that company's president, Ootsu Toshiyuki, who had returned to attend to business matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.49,0:07:29.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Using a weapon in his possession...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.41,0:07:32.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He threatened that same person to open the door of the safe in the room...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:36.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And utilizing a glass ashtray that was also in the room, struck the victim's head three times until he was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.37,0:07:41.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He then stole the 12,000,000 yen deposited in the safe, and escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.09,0:07:46.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Therefore, we request that the defendant be charged under Article 240 of the Penal Code, Robbery-Murder...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.97,0:07:49.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And sentenced to life in prison with hard labor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.89,0:07:55.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does the defendant admit to the prosecution's accusation?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.56,0:07:57.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or do you deny it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.14,0:08:01.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only entered to steal...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.11,0:08:02.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As far as intention to kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.73,0:08:03.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your Honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.28,0:08:05.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Proceed, counselor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.24,0:08:09.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The accusation is robbery-murder...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.41,0:08:11.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the defendant did not intend to murder the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:12.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Therefore I would like to raise an objection.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.95,0:08:16.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he denies the charge of robbery-murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.50,0:08:23.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe it would be more appropriate to change the charge from Article 240 to Article 205, Assault Leading to Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.84,0:08:27.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The defense appears to have an objection with the prosecution's accusation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.97,0:08:29.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have any concerns?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.43,0:08:31.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.01,0:08:34.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason the defendant chose Ootsu Real Estate...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.89,0:08:35.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.85,0:08:40.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was just that while I was looking for a building to enter and steal from...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.69,0:08:42.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I happened to come across that building by chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.06,0:08:44.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.32,0:08:46.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was just a coincidence that you chose to steal from Ootsu Real Estate...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:51.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you contend you had no existing grudge whatsoever against the victim Ootsu Toshiyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.20,0:08:53.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is all of this correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:54.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.91,0:08:57.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder what Prosecutor Kujou is trying to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.70,0:08:59.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your Honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.71,0:09:02.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The prosecution's aim with this line of questioning is unclear!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.29,0:09:04.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.71,0:09:08.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The defendant is familiar with a female by the name of Endou Noriko, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.09,0:09:11.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.68,0:09:14.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no reason you would forget your only daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.35,0:09:16.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.27,0:09:19.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.60,0:09:24.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was only eight years old when he divorced his ex-wife twenty years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.11,0:09:27.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I wonder what that has to do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.07,0:09:29.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it that you can't answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.99,0:09:30.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Objection!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.78,0:09:39.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The prosecution only seeks to put the defendant at unease by bringing up the name of a blood relative!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.45,0:09:44.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that daughter relevant to the court in any way?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.42,0:09:45.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:51.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Endou Noriko runs a snack stand in another building that Ootsu Real Estate manages.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.17,0:09:55.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It has been rumored that she was involved with the victim, Ootsu Toshiyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.39,0:10:02.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're saying it was not by coincidence the defendant broke into the building that became the crime scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.18,0:10:02.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.64,0:10:08.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We also have testimony to the effect that the defendant held a grudge against the victim because of his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.36,0:10:09.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.53,0:10:11.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.07,0:10:14.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, shall we ask the person in question?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.07,0:10:17.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since she is in the visitor's gallery, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.53,0:10:19.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can have her come out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.37,0:10:25.04,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Endou Noriko (28)\NInoue Takashi's Daughter
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.96,0:10:25.04,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.63,0:10:27.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Noriko...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.30,0:10:33.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So this is the card the Madonna had hidden up her sleeve?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.76,0:10:39.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's necessary, we are prepared to have Endou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} testify as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.28,0:10:56.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it's true what the prosecutor said?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.11,0:10:57.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.16,0:10:59.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was deceived by that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:05.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said sweet things such as how he would allow me to keep the shop, and took terrible advantage of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.17,0:11:08.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When did you get into contact with your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.29,0:11:12.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I reunited with him nearly two years ago when my mother passed away from illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.21,0:11:16.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ever since, he would occasionally stop by my shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.80,0:11:19.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you told him about Ootsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.47,0:11:24.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he'd get consolation money out of him for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:27.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's certainly turned into an unfavorable situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.56,0:11:29.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.56,0:11:34.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because, if he held a grudge against the other party and hit him as many as three times...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:37.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one would believe him even if he said he didn't intend to kill the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.32,0:11:39.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.55,0:11:42.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lastly, I'd like for you to answer me truthfully...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.95,0:11:47.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you also think your father murdered Ootsu Toshiyuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.50,0:11:52.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, Daddy likes stealing, but he's not someone who would kill a person!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.55,0:11:54.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.67,0:11:59.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like the battle to come will be an intense one this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.19,0:12:15.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.86,0:12:17.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dozing off again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.78,0:12:22.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just resting my eyes while thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.28,0:12:23.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's dozing off?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.24,0:12:26.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, have you hit upon it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.12,0:12:29.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A good idea you can use to help Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.62,0:12:32.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.88,0:12:37.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taking on this sort of case, it's Eri's own fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:44.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The defendant had a motive to murder, and on top of that his fingerprints were clearly on the dial of the safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.35,0:12:47.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How is somebody supposed to defend against that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.35,0:12:52.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I wonder why the dial on the safe was the only place his fingerprints were found?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.08,0:12:55.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for that, he probably snuck in wearing gloves!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.03,0:13:01.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, since gloves get in the way when it comes to precise tasks such as turning the dial on a safe, he removed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.91,0:13:04.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's when the victim came in, and so using the ashtray...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.66,0:13:08.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, his fingerprints should also be on the ashtray since it was the weapon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.75,0:13:09.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.54,0:13:11.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since he'd taken his gloves off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:14.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there were no fingerprints left on the ashtray.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.42,0:13:18.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, of course he wiped his fingerprints off afterwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.59,0:13:19.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me see that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.13,0:13:23.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Read this part carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:28.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it written here that there are traces of it having been wiped down with an oil-stained cloth?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.27,0:13:31.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's so, why didn't he wipe down the safe as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.10,0:13:33.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.44,0:13:37.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He accidentally killed someone, so in his haste, he fled and forgot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.86,0:13:38.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.40,0:13:42.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I wonder when he stole the money from the safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:46.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, after he committed the murder, he opened the safe again, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.08,0:13:48.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you just say he fled in haste?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.29,0:13:50.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.41,0:13:53.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somehow, it seems mismatched, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.29,0:13:54.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.46,0:13:57.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Criminals do all kinds of things that don't make sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.71,0:14:00.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that just a sophism?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.80,0:14:01.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.55,0:14:02.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm getting out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.88,0:14:06.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Dad, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.43,0:14:10.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.42,0:14:16.90,Signs,,0,0,0,,List of Articles Found at the Crime Scene\N1. Glass Ashtray\N2. 1 Pair of Army Cotton Gloves\N3. Eyeglasses screw\N4. Golf Ball
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.13,0:14:37.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.25,0:14:38.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.84,0:14:40.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.84,0:14:42.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, just something...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.09,0:14:48.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You came to the scene of the crime to see if there was anything you could do to help Kisaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.30,0:14:49.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.05,0:14:49.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:53.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Great Detective sure has a lot of free time, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.48,0:14:54.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.77,0:14:57.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kisaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}, you came to investigate the crime scene as well, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.77,0:14:58.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.69,0:15:01.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm getting permission from the building manager right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:07.41,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Akiyama Takuya (56) Building Manager
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:06.11,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.11,0:15:07.41,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,This way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.20,0:15:13.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mister, you were the first person to discover the company president?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.70,0:15:15.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, my boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.16,0:15:17.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could we hear a detailed account of what happened at that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:19.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.38,0:15:24.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On that night, at around 9:00, I was watching a baseball game on TV when...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.39,0:15:30.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.51,0:15:33.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you seen Dad—no, I mean, Mr. President?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.64,0:15:38.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I made my rounds at 8:00, no one was in the office...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.65,0:15:39.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.86,0:15:44.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When he left my restaurant a bit ago, he said he was coming back to the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.19,0:15:46.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, he must've come in through one of the emergency exits.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.99,0:15:51.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, the door to the office is locked, and there was no answer even though I called for him many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.53,0:15:54.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't he be in the rear office?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.58,0:15:58.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I came to drop off the reading glasses he left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.42,0:16:01.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but could you come and open the door for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.59,0:16:02.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.71,0:16:08.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Arima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} you mentioned was President Ootsu's adopted son-in-law, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.13,0:16:09.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.97,0:16:13.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He runs a nearby Italian restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:16.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it was this door that was locked, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.94,0:16:20.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I used this spare key to open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.66,0:16:31.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sure doesn't look like he's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.74,0:16:36.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.83,0:16:38.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's me, Masahiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.79,0:16:41.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.75,0:16:42.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.42,0:16:43.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's someone there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.63,0:16:49.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.01,0:16:50.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.34,0:16:53.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone inside is being beaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.68,0:16:54.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.27,0:16:57.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The key for the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.39,0:16:59.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The company president is the only one with the key to this door!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.85,0:17:00.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.85,0:17:01.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Move aside please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.69,0:17:06.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.28,0:17:09.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.44,0:17:10.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.95,0:17:12.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, please hurry and call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.37,0:17:13.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.46,0:17:24.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The company president's office is over there, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.13,0:17:29.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, this door is locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.22,0:17:32.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is in possession of the key to this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.47,0:17:34.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.43,0:17:36.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.60,0:17:40.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Kisaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, the attorney I mentioned on the phone and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.81,0:17:42.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Detective Mouri Kogoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.23,0:17:46.65,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Arima Masahiko (35)\NProprietor of an Italian Restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.73,0:17:45.36,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,You're the famous...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.69,0:17:46.96,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.36,0:17:49.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, apologies for interrupting your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.24,0:17:53.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were wondering if you would let us take a look in the company president's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.74,0:17:56.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, is this room not being used right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.62,0:18:00.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though the police have already completed their investigation...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.87,0:18:04.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since it was the room in which Dad died under such circumstances...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.42,0:18:07.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's hard to say what we'll do with it from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.84,0:18:08.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.88,0:18:11.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just as the police left it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:12.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.02,0:18:26.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, Arima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.77,0:18:29.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where was it that the victim fell?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.82,0:18:31.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.28,0:18:33.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was right around here, in front of the safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.28,0:18:36.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was on the floor, cradling his head in his arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.20,0:18:37.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.08,0:18:39.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's how it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.49,0:18:41.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"That's how it was"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.20,0:18:47.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely, Inoue was discovered by the victim as he was trying to open the safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.29,0:18:49.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The defendant had already stated as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.88,0:18:51.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's important is what happened afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.55,0:18:57.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inoue used a knife or something he had hidden on him to threaten the victim into opening the safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.55,0:19:01.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, when it was opened, he used the ashtray, and from behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.77,0:19:03.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Struck him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.85,0:19:07.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're not saying the defendant is lying, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.06,0:19:11.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if he wanted you believe that he was innocent, that's probably it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.11,0:19:14.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way to defend a defendant if you don't believe him, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.49,0:19:20.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can say all the neat phrases you want, but you're only going to get thrashed by that Madonna!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.67,0:19:31.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say Mister, where you saw the culprit from...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:32.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was it this tiny window?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.01,0:19:33.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.96,0:19:34.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.68,0:19:42.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.81,0:19:44.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just what are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.98,0:19:48.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle Kogoro, could you stand in front of the safe again for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.98,0:19:49.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.06,0:19:51.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.03,0:19:55.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.44,0:19:57.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just wait there for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.41,0:20:00.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:02.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah-le!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:06.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From here, Uncle is hidden by the screen and I can't see him at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.71,0:20:08.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.21,0:20:10.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.21,0:20:11.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.44,0:20:12.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.71,0:20:14.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What I saw wasn't over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.38,0:20:18.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was just the shadow of a person I saw reflected over on this wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.20,0:20:20.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A shadow reflected on the wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.26,0:20:21.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.14,0:20:24.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time, the lights in the room were off...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.81,0:20:30.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I saw the culprit's shadow reflected by the neon lights shining in from the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.85,0:20:34.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The shadow of someone hitting Ootsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.61,0:20:41.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And after that, I also heard the sound of Ootsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} falling to the ground, so there's no mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.95,0:20:43.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to ask you one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.45,0:20:47.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You did not, then, see Defendant Inoue actually striking the victim, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.12,0:20:49.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Miss Attorney...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.83,0:20:51.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not an important difference, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.46,0:20:54.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit even said that he struck him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.92,0:20:56.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, Arima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.42,0:20:59.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Merely seeing a shadow of someone striking another...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.13,0:21:02.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is completely different from seeing the actual person striking him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.30,0:21:06.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter the circumstances, until the defendant is tried and a guilty verdict comes down in court...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.39,0:21:09.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He is still considered a defendant, and not a culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.31,0:21:14.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When such sad feelings are involved, everyone tends to confuse the two.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.61,0:21:16.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.69,0:21:17.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.07,0:21:21.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This clock's stopped, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.99,0:21:27.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a prize that the late company president won in a golf tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.66,0:21:30.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was placed there as a commemoration ornament, and isn't usually used.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.54,0:21:34.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, if you could come over here a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.75,0:21:35.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.34,0:21:36.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.84,0:21:39.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The combination to the safe in question...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.92,0:21:42.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did anyone else know it outside the victim?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.18,0:21:44.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, only my father knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.14,0:21:47.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For security reasons...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.47,0:21:49.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn't even tell the accounting heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.48,0:21:53.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're in the way, just loitering around!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.86,0:21:56.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.61,0:22:00.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, I understand it now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.03,0:22:01.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The trick behind this case!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.67,0:22:06.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The shadow of someone beating someone else that Akiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} supposedly saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.97,0:22:08.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the sound of something having fallen...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.72,0:22:11.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Using this trick, it could all be manufactured!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.89,0:22:15.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the one who set this trick up...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.23,0:22:17.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could only be that person!
